notes:
IMPORTANT:

- In order for Vortex to find games their directories must be added manually under "Settings > Games > Add Search Directory" and then a full scan must be run under "Games > Scan". Adding the directory <i>Z:\home\$USER\.steam\steam\steamapps\common</i> (where $USER is your user) will allow Vortex to see all your Steam/Steam Play games;

KNOWN BUGS/LIMITATIONS:

- After clicking "manage" on a discovered game an error may pop up. This error can be safely ignored;
